      "content": "i mean yeah, people say that stuff to feel better but it doesnt change the math of it. if the universe is just going to end and everything we do is temporary, then there's no real objective difference between breathing and not breathing. it's just two different states of being. how can anyone say one is better than the other if the outcome is always zero?",
